<item>
            <title>[SOLR-41] PATCH: HyphenatedWordsFilter, Factory and test</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-41</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the plain text is extracted from documents, we will often have many words hyphenated and broken into two lines. This is often the case with documents where narrow text columns are used, such as newsletters.&lt;br/&gt;
In order to increase searching efficiency, this filter unites hyphenated words broken in two lines.&lt;br/&gt;
This filter has to be used together with the WordDelimiterFilter having catenateWords=1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
